== About me 
Before coming to Fudan, I completed my Ph.D. in School of Physics at [http://www.bit.edu.cn/ Beijing Institute of Technology], 
where I worked with [http://physics.bit.edu.cn/szdw/zzjzg/fg/lyl/index.htm Prof. Yulong Liu]. Before that, I received B.E. in School of Information and Communication Engineering from [http://www.njit.edu.cn/ Nanjing Institute of Technology].



== News
- May 2021: "Exact matrix completion based on low rank Hankel structure in the Fourier domain" (joint work with Weiguo Gao and Ke Wei) is accepted to Applied and Computational Harmonic Analysis.
- New release, Oct 2020: "Vectorized Hankel Lift: A Convex Approach for Blind Super-Resolution of Point Sources" (joint work with Weiguo Gao, Sihan Mao and Ke Wei).
- New grant, Sep 2020: "Recovery and blind deconvolution of spectrally sparse signal based on low rankness
". Funding Agency: NSFC 12001108, PI: Jan 2021 - Dec 2023.